    <h1 class="mb-4">AI SEO Agency Comparison UK 2026</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-text-muted mb-8">Last updated: April 2026 | Based on public information, published methodologies, and client outcomes</p>

    <img src="/images/content/stat-77-percent.svg" alt="UK AI visibility research data" class="w-full rounded-xl mb-8 mt-6" loading="lazy">
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Choosing an AI SEO agency is difficult because the discipline is new and every agency describes what they do differently. Some call it GEO. Some call it AI search optimisation. Some say "AI-first SEO." The terminology is inconsistent, which makes comparison harder than it should be.</p>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-10">This page compares the leading UK agencies side by side on the things that actually matter: what they focus on, what methodology they use, how many AI platforms they cover, what they charge, and what type of business they suit best.</p>

