    <h2 class="mb-6">Detailed Comparison</h2>

    <div class="space-y-8">
      <!-- Rank4AI -->
      <div class="card-teal-border">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-3">
          <h2 class="!text-xl text-teal">Rank4AI</h2>
          <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-accent bg-off-white px-3 py-1 rounded-full">AI Search Specialist</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-3">The only agency on this list that works exclusively on AI search. No SEO services, no PPC, no social media management. Every client engagement is about AI search visibility. The Five Signal Model provides a structured framework for understanding why AI recommends some businesses and not others. Data from 1,400+ UK audits means recommendations are based on observed patterns, not theory. Colchester, Essex. From GBP 800/mo.</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted"><span class="highlight">Differentiator:</span> 100% AI search focus. No distractions from other services. Original UK research data.</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted mt-1">rank4ai.co.uk</p>
      </div>

      <!-- AwarenessAI -->
      <div class="card">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-3">
          <h2 class="!text-xl text-teal">AwarenessAI</h2>
          <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-text-muted bg-off-white px-3 py-1 rounded-full">AI Visibility Platform</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-3">More of a product than a traditional agency. The dashboard gives businesses ongoing visibility into how AI platforms talk about their brand. Useful for tracking changes over time and measuring impact of optimisation work. The agency services layer strategy on top of the monitoring data. SaaS pricing from GBP 100/mo makes it the most affordable entry point on this list.</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted"><span class="highlight">Differentiator:</span> Productised approach with dashboard. Lowest entry price. Ongoing monitoring built in.</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted mt-1">awarenessai.co.uk</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Varn -->
      <div class="card">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-3">
          <h2 class="!text-xl text-teal">Varn</h2>
          <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-text-muted bg-off-white px-3 py-1 rounded-full">SEO + GEO Agency</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-3">Best option for businesses that want AI search and traditional SEO from the same agency. 15+ years means deep SEO expertise. Google Premier Partner status adds credibility. The AI Visibility Framework is a genuine addition, not a rebrand. Innovation team keeps R&D active. Particularly strong in healthcare and pharmaceutical sectors where trust and compliance signals are critical for AI recommendations.</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted"><span class="highlight">Differentiator:</span> Combined SEO + AI search under one roof. Healthcare sector specialism. Google Premier Partner.</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted mt-1">varn.co.uk</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Found -->
      <div class="card">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-3">
          <h2 class="!text-xl text-teal">Found</h2>
          <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-text-muted bg-off-white px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Digital Marketing Agency</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-3">Best option for large brands that want AI search integrated into a full digital marketing strategy. Luminr technology provides proprietary data on visibility across search and AI platforms. Agency-scale resources mean they can handle complex, multi-channel implementations. The "AI-first Everysearch" positioning signals genuine investment in AI search rather than adding a service line. London based.</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted"><span class="highlight">Differentiator:</span> Proprietary Luminr technology. Full-service digital integration. Enterprise resources.</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted mt-1">found.co.uk</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Screaming Frog -->
      <div class="card">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-3">
          <h2 class="!text-xl text-teal">Screaming Frog</h2>
          <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-text-muted bg-off-white px-3 py-1 rounded-full">SEO Agency + Tool Maker</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-3">Best option for businesses that need deep technical work done on their site for AI readiness. The team that built the SEO Spider understands crawling, indexing, and content parsing at a level most agencies cannot match. Day-rate pricing makes them suitable for focused projects - get the technical foundation right, then move to ongoing optimisation with another provider if needed. Henley-on-Thames.</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted"><span class="highlight">Differentiator:</span> Unmatched technical depth. Day-rate pricing for project work. Tool-maker credibility.</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted mt-1">screamingfrog.co.uk</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Exposure Ninja -->
      <div class="card">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-3">
          <h2 class="!text-xl text-teal">Exposure Ninja</h2>
          <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-text-muted bg-off-white px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Digital Marketing Agency</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-3">Best option for SMEs wanting an accessible, low-risk entry into AI search. Free website review gives you an initial read without commitment. Their podcast and blog show genuine engagement with AI search as a topic, not just a sales angle. B Corp certified. UK and US offices. The AI search service sits within a broader digital marketing offering.</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted"><span class="highlight">Differentiator:</span> SME focus. Free review as entry point. Content marketing demonstrates real knowledge. B Corp.</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted mt-1">exposureninja.com</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 p-6 bg-off-white rounded-xl border border-border">
      <h2 class="!text-lg mb-3">How to Use This Comparison</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-3">Start with what you need. If you want dedicated AI search with no distractions, look at the specialists (Rank4AI, AwarenessAI). If you want AI search alongside traditional SEO, look at agencies with genuine AI methodology (Varn, Found). If you need technical foundations fixed first, consider Screaming Frog on a day-rate basis.</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed">Ask every agency you speak to: what is your specific methodology for AI search? How many AI platforms do you test? Can you show me research or case studies? If the answers are vague, the capability is probably vague too.</p>
    </div>
  </div>


